article_title: Tea Party Express reveals its own CPAC ‘Oscar selfie’ [Photoshop] – twitchy.com
article_text:
Ellen Degeneres’ Twitter-breaking “Oscar selfie” has already been topped by the 2nd and 95th Airlift Squadrons at Pope Field, North Carolina, but today brings another contender. The Tea Party Express has put together its own CPAC version with Rand Paul holding the camera phone.

How does this not have 3M RTs yet? RT @TeaPartyExpress: #CPACSelfie #CPAC2014 pic.twitter.com/Jq3KRQ0WLa — Slade Sohmer (@Slade) March 8, 2014
